OL,4,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,5,     GThis episode explores the ways in
OL,6,     Gwhich men deal with pain and
OL,7,     Ginjury, from a cyst on the knee
OL,8,     Gto a dislocated shoulder that
OL,9,     Gtakes a five-strong team to pull
OL,10,     Gback into place.
OL,11,G2305F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GNineteen-year-old fitness fanatic
OL,13,     GJosh is flown to King's after
OL,14,     Gbeing injured in a canal barge
OL,15,     Gaccident. And two best friends
OL,16,     Gare recovering from a Sunday
OL,17,     Gnight out clubbing.
